<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Cryptocrush - Learn Cryptography & Ciphers</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset and base */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #0b1a3d; /* dark blue */
      color: #e0e7ff; /* light text */
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    header {
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #83aaff;
      margin-bottom: 0.25em;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .slogan {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #a3bffa;
      margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    p.description {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #d1d9ff;
      margin-bottom: 2em;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-button {
      background: #3b5998; /* a rich blue */
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 89, 152, 0.5);
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #5a79c1;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(90, 121, 193, 0.7);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #667db6;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #83aaff;
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Cryptocrush</h1>
    <div class="slogan">Crack the Code. Master the Secrets.</div>
    <p class="description">
      Welcome to Cryptocrush, your gateway to the fascinating world of cryptography and ciphers. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned codebreaker, explore interactive lessons, historical insights, and hands-on challenges to unlock the secrets behind secure communication. Dive in and start crushing codes today!
    </p>
    <a href="#get-started" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
  </header>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Cryptocrush. All rights reserved.  
    <br />
    <a href="https://github.com/cryoxero/cryptocrush" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on GitHub</a>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

